#LightGBM

# Evaluate each model
results = []
names = []
scoring = 'accuracy'

for name, model in models:
    cv_results = cross_val_score(model, X2, y2, cv=5, scoring=scoring)
    results.append(cv_results)
    names.append(name)
    msg = "%s: %f (%f)" % (name, cv_results.mean(), cv_results.std())
    print(msg)
